          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1614006639222-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put the tray in the oven for 10 min or until the tomatoes have softened</p><p>Meanwhile, add the<strong> potato mixture</strong>,<strong> egg<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> and 1.5 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[3 tbsp] </span><strong>milk</strong> to the mashed potatoes and mix until well combined – this is your <strong>batter</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1614006662248-x200.jpg",
