            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a knob of<strong> butter </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, dollop 6 <span class=\"text-danger\">[12]</span> spoonfuls of <strong>batter </strong>into the pan then and cook, covered, for 3-4 min or until the mixture looks set on top</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Do this in batches!</p><p>Once set, flip and cook for 1-2 min on the other side – these are your <strong>boxty</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1614006683593-x200.jpg",
